snippet: The New Juilliard Ensemble presented works on Tuesday by two composers in their 20s, Michael Ippolito and Molly Joyce, alongside concertos by Robin de Raaff and Valentin Bibik.
lead_paragraph: The New Juilliard Ensemble presented works on Tuesday by two composers in their 20s, Michael Ippolito and Molly Joyce, alongside concertos by Robin de Raaff and Valentin Bibik.
